_sText:
This is the third (and probably final) release of surf_aircontrol. As compared to version 1 i've added a few more routes, cubemaps, fixed some bugs, and a few other things.

This is a pure surf map with no weapons at start. Surf down the course (its long and fast) to the end (if you make it :P ) and then pick up a gun and shoot the other team. Enjoy!
